      "title": "One lakh Sri Lankans who have gone abroad",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "More than one and a half lakh people have gone abroad from Sri Lanka since last January.",
        "An Indian media has reported that one lakh 767 people have gone abroad personally and 55 thousand 411 people have gone abroad through the bureau."
      ],
